/**
 * @mainpage Multi Mini-Games Lobby
 *
 * @section intro_sec Introduction
 *
 * Welcome to the Multi Mini-Games Lobby documentation.
 * This project provides a central hub for managing and launching multiple
 * mini-games from a unified interface.
 *
 * @section features_sec Features
 *
 * - Game selection and management
 * - Player session handling
 * - Score tracking across games
 * - Seamless integration with multiple mini-game modules
 *
 * @section arch_sec Architecture
 *
 * The lobby system acts as a central coordinator between the user interface
 * and the various mini-game modules. It handles:
 * - Game registration and discovery
 * - State management for active sessions
 * - Communication between games and the main application
 *
 * @section author_sec Author
 *
 * Maxime CHAUVEAU
 *
 * @section date_sec Date
 *
 * February 25, 2026
 *
 * @section version_sec Version
 *
 * 1.0.0
 */
